# Note: Unless you want a specific reviewer's expertise, please send CLs to
# chromium-webapps-reviews@google.com rather than to specific
# individuals. These CLs will be automatically reassigned to a reviewer within
# about 5 minutes. This approach helps our team to load-balance incoming
# reviews. Googlers can read more about this at go/gwsq-gerrit.
#
# To join the rotation modify the OWNERS and gwsq files in
# go/gwsq-gerrit-webapps. Add yourself in the ShadowedReviewers list first
# before becoming the main reviewer if you're new to the team.
#
# If you are in the ShadowedReviewers list for go/gwsq-gerrit-webapps, please
# assign to an owner from the names below after your LGTM, so that they
# can allow the code to land.
chromium-webapps-reviews@google.com

# The find-owners plugin does not support groups, so the actual c/b/web_applications/
# reviewers are listed below but tagged with {LAST_RESORT_SUGGESTION} so that
# Gerrit will preferentially suggest the review alias above.
